{"tid":278961,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃洋達：「太博段錄音我完全唔知情，我唔建議佢咁講嘢。」","createTime":"2017-06-11T00:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T10:56:31.000Z","uid":28938,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a585009a709b19bafd90d9c5d494d32ed13f8a0","tid":278961,"uid":28938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T00:27:27.000Z","msg":"黃洋達：<br />\n<br />\n6月11日回應<br />\n「太博段錄音我完全唔知情，我唔建議佢咁樣講嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n6月12日回應<br />\n「唔關我事，我當日唔在場；佢唔代表我哋熱血公民。」<br />\n<br />\n6月13日回應<br />\n「我幾時都叫熱血公民小心言論，松泰今次真係幫唔過。」<br />\n<br />\n6月14日回應<br />\n「做人最緊要正直！我地熱血公民同鄭松泰今日開始唔再係同路人。大家撐佢即係我地敵人。」"},{"pid":"6bb188bf4250540228c20ff168976acf46970311","tid":278961,"uid":71392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T00:30:47.000Z","msg":"其實佢個幾句野，黃洋逹自己都啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efacd2bfbf24077f6049a795b1acc5c6cf748b1d","tid":278961,"uid":28938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T00:30:49.000Z","msg":"6月15日<br />\n「忍口唔出聲係因為要計劃旅行。」<br />\n<br />\n6月16日<br />\n「想當年五區公投已經知道鄭松泰係反骨仔。」"},{"pid":"10229b00c10b58caacf64cbf02973b37d1341a56","tid":278961,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:07:19.000Z","msg":"咁係邊個放料呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b3bdda3e09a77fd40663bd53ce5d876a616140","tid":278961,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4a8ae09824399908b63a7c4f61165e898461f0","tid":278961,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133458f777d84313517ef50eb52b49cab515b010","tid":27896