":278961,"uid":61279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T09:40:17.000Z","msg":"光頭達真係會為左自保而同泰博割蓆都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f0f195ba4507519a9c45e4484340acca00cac0","tid":278961,"uid":4389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T09:45:12.000Z","msg":"黃洋達：「我連電話都打唔通比鄭松泰，何況我又退出左熱血公民。而家佢將熱公民政黨化，我專注熱血時報、兩者已經分家，所以鄭松泰嘅言論與我無關。」<br />\n<br />\n繼續搬龍門話兩者分家咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447fb51fd6b067bb1e9bb2f4b5a0e77d3dc7dc86","tid":278961,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃洋達：「我連電話都打唔通比鄭松泰，何況我又退出左熱血公民。而家佢將熱公民政黨化，我專注熱血時報、兩者已經分家，所以鄭松泰嘅言論與我無關。」<br />\n<br />\n繼續搬龍門話兩者分家咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}